snippet.title: Used - Better On My Own
snippet.description:
Stream / Download:  https://fanlink.to/betteronmyown

Belgium-based prodigy Used is not your run-of-the-mill drum&bass producer. He plays multiple instruments and writes and sings his own songs. He grew up in Netsky-territory and spent his early years dj‚Äôing while riding the waves of the well-documented Belgian jump-up scene. He is all about drum&bass but loves to draw from all corners of its spectrum, while always aiming at the dancefloor as well as at his audience‚Äôs feels. Once again, in Better On My Own, the man exposes his feelings on top of supercatchy bassline melodies that will get stuck in your ear as well as keep the dancefloor shaking. After self releasing and the joining Macky Gee on Down 2 Earth Musik, he now touches down on Rampage Recordings ahead of his set at the world‚Äôs biggest drum&bass and dubstep party, where we‚Äôll expect this tune to be one of the highlights.
